Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Senpai--the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.61,0:00:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ocean! Ocean! Ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Niiice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The beach in summer makes everyone open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these four doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It all began one afternoon a week earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,right here in this café.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:01:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, folks: here comes\NUzaki-chan Wants to Hang Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,this is our new part-timer: Hana Uzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to be part of the team!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You were so gung-ho on me quitting\Nso I could get some peace!{Another episode on: My translator sister shouldn't be this wrong! "I told you numerous times to give up on starting as a part timer here so my peace wouldn't be disturbed!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:03:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, don't be a hater. We'll have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I'm here in part because\NI wanted to see that hater face of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,With summer break around the corner and all,\NI wanted a little more spending money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked the owner and got his immediate okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be fun,\Nso I figured I'd hire her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Sakurai, you may not like Hana,{"you may not like hana here"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but she is the one who\Ncame to me looking for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be wrong for you to try to stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just show her the ropes for now.\NOne learns by teaching, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure about this, Senpai?\NThink you can teach me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When a customer comes in,\Nshow them to their seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Regulars often head to their\Nfavorite spot before you take them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a practice customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here: ice water and a hand towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first thing\Nwe bring to each new customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait till you see they're seated,\Nthen bring these out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me know when you're ready to order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful not to make a menu-reading\Ncustomer feel rushed or pressured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you take their order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it usually goes. Next we'll--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are all the jokes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any! What exactly did you expect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This act is going on forever!\NYou gotta toss in a little joke or three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What act?! We're not putting on a skit here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! You're getting\Npaid for this--take it seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's your café, Mr. Employer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been showing her how\Nit's done since before you arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This right here was all about winding you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you going anywhere over summer break?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Nowhere in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking forward\Nto this game that's coming out--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan to hole up at home as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You do that all year long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna waste your\Nprecious summer break on games?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man... this is shaping up\Nto be the best summer ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This athletic shut-in is just hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go to the beach! Or a pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's settled! A done deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't done any swimming since\Nyou graduated high school, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Heard you were working together\Nand came by to see for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this looks like a fun conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hana!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here! Over this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What a terrible sight.\NThose things are weapons.{"I've witnessed a terrible sight", or you know, you can go for ""vietnam flashbacks ahaha}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We rented an umbrella and\Nset out a beach blanket! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish the bossman could have come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not after he threw out his back.{you can add a "can't help it" before the sentence}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sakaki? He came a little earlier,\Nsaid he was gonna check out our lodging.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle transportation and lodging.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You sure, Itsuhito?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! Let's all go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Beach! Beach! Beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where do you get off--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel, but... it's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you in good conscience send them off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the two of them--no regrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So now it's up to me to watch over those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where's Sakurai? Wasn't he with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai? He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's far! How did he wind up out there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He got so hyped up gazing at the water,{"He seemed like being hyped after gazing at the water", just an alternative}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,then went running into it full tilt\Nlike he just couldn't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That jerk will stop at nothing\Nto get his alone time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never swum in the ocean before--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the waves make it\Na little different than a pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardcore much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Sakurai, you don't need goggles\Nat the beach--let alone a swim cap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a lifeguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,See? It's like I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole swim-club look turns\Npeople off, so let's skip it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, we're here to have fun!\NThis is leisure time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget all about swim club for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's super ticked off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And why'd you leave Hana behind\Nand go swimming alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,See, if you're all alone, so is Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What if someone hits on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you be responsible if something happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy she came with has to look out for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yessir...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can start with swimsuit compliments.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it'll come easy to you,\Nbut that's what you get for going solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You look really good in that swimsuit.\NJust wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky blue suits your personal image,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a shock. Looking at me\Nso seriously from so close up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Doofus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Senpai? The dolphin's almost ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear! Did he say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, nothing! Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Covering up her embarrassment, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Will that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I remain somewhat suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Enjoying yourselves? I brought a snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, a watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'll use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right--it's time for...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...a seaside standby: the watermelon piñata!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never done it before!\NWe're making memories, Sak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, blindfold's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist. Come at me--from any direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually more fun to be on the guiding end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the mis guiding end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,First let's blindside him\Nand drop-kick him into the ocean!{"first let's take adventage of his defenseles state..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You go there first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of games do you play, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Uzaki, you get right on Sak there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on--can I get a video\Nof this with my phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You realize I can\Nhear everything you're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on then, Sak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, Senpai, you're practically a sitting duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Over a short distance: up, down, left, right, B!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you start? Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Down, up, down, B, down-right,\Nup-left, B, up, up-left, A!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you feeding me\Ninputs for fighting-game moves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, quit screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Right, right, up, down, left, B!\NLeft, down, right, up, A, B!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, is she in her element.\NNothing left for us to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9}That doesn't make any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's what I call a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Start by walking forward, Sakurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5\blur3\fs75\pos(252,267)\fnOpen Sans Extrabold}True
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5\blur3\fs75\fnOpen Sans Extrabold\pos(1641,147)}True
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A little to the right--to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, Senpai! Up, X, down, B, L, Y, R, A!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5\blur3\fs75\fnOpen Sans Extrabold\pos(474,246)}Not an option
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Uzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? A jellyfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come on--that's just way too convenient!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me where to go! Where's that melon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you grabbing it right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please move first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax. The place is just up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so pouty about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I'm not pouty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was bound to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, forget it! Where's that damn watermelon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, so that was the watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He is such a doofus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When you said you'd handle the lodging...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your summer home?{"so you owned a summer house"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in. Pick whichever room you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were rich, Sakaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you had a summer home,\Nbut this is the first I've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I invited you last year--you just didn't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:14:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And my parents are the rich ones, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Check it out, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A rich person's light switch!{Light switches are the kind of rich people's ones", both same meaning but well, this is more literal, for context}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! The intercom has a camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It's one of those click-pull things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your standard for "rich," anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Take anything you want from the fridge.\NI stocked it up for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Senpai: meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You do like meat, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course I do! After all, it is meat!{vegan trigger, delet dis -aria}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm, delish! Cookouts are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's a showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two, you can do that any old time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:15:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summer break!\NSleeping away from home! And nighttime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That calls for a certain... activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To the back hills!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we did what you said\Nand followed you here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awfully dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going to build a campfire?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, it's a little clichéd,\Nbut it's just not summer without...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...a test of courage! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this bluff up ahead, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear it! I'm out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives, Sak? Not into this kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't play horror games\Nor watch horror flicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You struck a pose to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's desperately trying to avoid danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I seriously didn't know it was\Na problem for you. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... while it's great to be honest and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe it wasn't such a hot idea\Nto announce your own weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So scary stuff is too much for you, eh, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, I had no idea{too}. Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock that off, Uzaki. It was all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it too early to raise the white flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He really can't deal with scary stuff, can he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoink!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Woohoo! Got your phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to air all your dirty laundry\Nfor everyone to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Give that back! I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to catch me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, you're fast, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit going further in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured we'd all go in together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I was picturing it the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Senpai, I'm so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well. Shall we go after them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me not to meddle, to watch over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought I'd just create\Nthe right conditions instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Conditions for them to turn\Ninto something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. I figured that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But when every move those\Ntwo make is so unexpected...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't go so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you go to such lengths?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sak's a great guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's so damn serious,\Nand awkward, and bad at making friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and a loner...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And while I know it's none of my business,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish his college life could be more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, it's kind of\Na waste, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That and... other reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Other reasons, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, Senpai. Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakaki and Ami are here, see? We'll all head back\Nand have some ice cream, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move another step.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice is so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm calling it off. Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go back and play games, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Play games...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesss! Look at that, Senpai! New high score!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you were going to play games!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakaki and Ami fell asleep, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we did have a really active day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's just tuckered out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, seeing his sleeping face\Nlike this gets me all restless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault for letting down your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,S-S-Senpai! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's a hugger, huh? Didn't see that coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, what a fright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Whoa, Senpai!\NYou're not secretly awake, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he wouldn't do this if he were awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I am the one who teased\Nthe scaredy cat and tired him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's okay for a little while, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for today... Just for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So I fell asleep in the\Nliving room after all that, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But man, it feels like\NI had a great night's sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You might want to invest\Nin one of those body pillows.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling we missed on\Nsomething extremely important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I'll get those two together for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I bet Kakyoin's soul\Nthat you'll fail yet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana Uzaki is becoming an adult!
